    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been super reliable for me. It\u2019s got that perfect balance of being well-loved but still looking and feeling fantastic on the road. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend adventure, this car is ready to go! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
