    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2002 BMW M3 (E46) features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS. Paired with a precise 6-speed Getrag manual and a factory limited-slip differential, the drivetrain remains tight and responsive. The chassis benefits from reinforced rear subframe mounts and refreshed bushings, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension maintain optimal geometry under load. Finished in Titanium Silver over Black Nappa leather, this example represents a mechanically robust driver's car with documented valve adjustments and rod bearing service. Minor cosmetic stone chips reflect its status as an engaging road machine rather than a museum piece.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
