    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and value. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though a discerning eye will find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the leather upholstery remains supple and free of tears, showing only light bolster wear on the driver's side. All electronic features, including the premium sound system and climate control, are fully functional. Mechanically, this car is robust; it has been serviced at regular intervals, with a recent oil change and brake inspection performed just last month. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the transmission shifts smoothly through every gear. It is a reliable, attractive daily driver that has been treated with respect and is ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
