      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies consistent care and reliable performance. This offering balances sophisticated engineering with a clean, professional presentation, ensuring a premium driving experience. Thoroughly inspected to meet our rigorous standards, it represents an exceptional value for the discerning motorist seeking both quality and longevity.",
      "price": 38500.0,
