      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable car for me and is still in really solid shape! It\u2019s super clean, drives smoothly, and is totally ready for its next adventure. You\u2019re going to love how it handles on the road\u2014it's been a joy to own!",
